      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures, version control, and regression test suite. Software quality documentation reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed via method of manufactured solutions for the Navier-Stokes solver and the power-law hemolysis transport equation. Observed convergence rates are consistent with formal order of accuracy."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI for hemolysis index below 4% on the medium mesh selected for production runs. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions from the FDA interlaboratory study are documented with controlled fluid temperature, hematocrit, and pump speed. Boundary conditions in the CFD model are set to match reported experimental values within stated tolerances."
    },
