      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Predicted hemolysis index compared against mean experimental values from five independent FDA interlaboratory participants. Relative error within 15% across all three operating points. Velocity profiles at impeller exit compared via PIV data with acceptable agreement."
